  "description": "Recipe mod made by GK1H.",
  "body": "Recipe mod made by GK1H.\n<h1>Features</h1>\n<h2>Bundle</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Bundle</strong></summary>\nBundle recipe, if Metal Bundles is loaded instead disables bundle recipe and replaces the leather bundle recipe from Metal Bundles.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Bundle/bundle.png\" alt=\"Bundle\">\n</details>\n<h2>Chain</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Chain</strong></summary>\nBetter chain recipe and chainmail armor recipes.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Chain/chain.png\" alt=\"Chain\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Chain/chainmail_helmet.png\" alt=\"Chainmail Helmet\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Chain/chainmail_chestplate.png\" alt=\"Chainmail Chestplate\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Chain/chainmail_leggings.png\" alt=\"Chainmail Leggings\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Chain/chainmail_boots.png\" alt=\"Chainmail Boots\">\n</details>\n<h2>Enchanted Golden Apple</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Enchanted Golden Apple</strong></summary>\nEnchanted golden apple recipes, including both using an apple and using a golden apple.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/enchanted_golden_apple.png\" alt=\"Enchanted Golden Apple\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_1.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 1\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_2.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 2\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_3.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 3\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_4.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 4\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_5.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 5\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_6.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 6\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_7.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 7\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Enchanted%20Golden%20Apple/golden_apple_enchant_8.png\" alt=\"Golden Apple Enchant 8\">\n</details>\n<h2>Heavy Core</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Heavy Core</strong></summary>\nHeavy core duplication recipe.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Heavy%20Core/heavy_core.png\" alt=\"Heavy Core\">\n</details>\n<h2>Horse Armor & Saddle</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Horse Armor & Saddle</strong></summary>\nHorse armor & saddle recipes, including modifying the leather horse armor recipe to match the other horse armor recipes.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Horse%20Armor%20%26%20Saddle/saddle.png\" alt=\"Saddle\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Horse%20Armor%20%26%20Saddle/leather_horse_armor.png\" alt=\"Leather Horse Armor\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Horse%20Armor%20%26%20Saddle/golden_horse_armor.png\" alt=\"Golden Horse Armor\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Horse%20Armor%20%26%20Saddle/iron_horse_armor.png\" alt=\"Iron Horse Armor\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Horse%20Armor%20%26%20Saddle/diamond_horse_armor.png\" alt=\"Diamond Horse Armor\">\n</details>\n<h2>Lead</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Lead</strong></summary>\nBackported lead recipe.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Lead/lead.png\" alt=\"Lead\">\n</details>\n<h2>Lodestone</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Lodestone</strong></summary>\nBackported lodestone recipe and if Advanced Netherite is loaded its lodestone recipes are removed.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Lodestone/lodestone.png\" alt=\"Lodestone\">\n</details>\n<h2>Netherite Ingot</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Netherite Ingot</strong></summary>\nNetherite ingot recipe.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Netherite%20Ingot/netherite.png\" alt=\"Netherite Ingot\">\n</details>\n<h2>Smithing</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Smithing</strong></summary>\nSmithing recipes for Metal Bundles, diamond bundle to netherite bundle, and Spiky Spikes, diamond spike to netherite spike.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Smithing/netherite_bundle.png\" alt=\"Netherite Bundle\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Smithing/netherite_spike.png\" alt=\"Netherite Spike\">\n</details>\n<h2>Tuff & Netherrack</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Tuff & Netherrack</strong></summary>\nTuff & netherrack recipes.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Tuff%20%26%20Netherrack/tuff.png\" alt=\"Tuff\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Tuff%20%26%20Netherrack/netherrack.png\" alt=\"Netherrack\">\n</details>\n<h2>Totem of Undying</h2>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Totem of Undying</strong></summary>\nTotem of Undying recipe.<br>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gameking1happy-Development/GK1H-Recipes/refs/heads/main/images/Totem%20of%20Undying/totem_of_undying.png\" alt=\"Totem Of Undying\">\n</details>\n<h1>Links</h1>\n<a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/gk1h-recipes\"><font color=\"#f16436\">CurseForge</font></a>",
